main event: Two brilliant white lights were observed at 45 degree intervals, with the first light changing from red to brilliant white and back to red. The objects were moving toward the North.
interesting points: A military jet had taken off from Blytheville AFB, Arkansas on a northbound course and would have passed near the point of observation.
The color of the first light changed from red to brilliant white then back to red.
The objects were moving toward the North.
No photographs or physical evidence were obtained.
